headline: Evercore ISI Group Maintains Outperform on Equinix, Raises Price Target to $1060
summary: Evercore ISI Group  analyst John Belton   maintains Equinix (NASDAQ:EQIX) with a Outperform and raises the price target from $960 to $1060.
